Dr. Ali Haidar Ahmed is a [[Maldives|Maldivian]] politician and currently a Minister of Housing Land and Urban Development.<ref>{{Cite web |title=Pres seeks parliamentary approval for new cabinet |url=https://avas.mv/en/137609 |access-date=2023-11-20 |website=avas.mv |language=en}}</ref> He also served as Housing Minister for a brief three months at the end of [[Maumoon Abdul Gayoom|Maumoon]]’s administration. <ref>{{Cite web |last=frontpage.mv |title=President Dr. Muizzu Has Appointed the New Cabinet |url=https://www.frontpage.mv/news/detail/787 |access-date=2023-11-20 |website=frontpage.mv |language=en}}</ref>

'''Dr. Ali Haidar Ahmed''' is a [[Maldives|Maldivian]] politician and currently a Minister of Housing Land and Urban Development.<ref>{{Cite web |title=Pres seeks parliamentary approval for new cabinet |url=https://avas.mv/en/137609 |access-date=2023-11-20 |website=avas.mv |language=en}}</ref> He also served as Housing Minister for a brief three months at the end of [[Maumoon Abdul Gayoom|Maumoon]]’s administration. <ref>{{Cite web |last=frontpage.mv |title=President Dr. Muizzu Has Appointed the New Cabinet |url=https://www.frontpage.mv/news/detail/787 |access-date=2023-11-20 |website=frontpage.mv |language=en}}</ref>
